## CI/CD Integration

### Setup for CI Systems
```bash
# On development machine
firebase login:ci
# → Copy the generated token

# In CI system, store token securely and use:
export FIREBASE_TOKEN="<your_token>"
firebase deploy
```

### Revoke Token
```bash
firebase logout --token <token>
```

